Title: A Batty Request
Description:
I'll gather a selection of our major trade goods before we head out for the meet up, but I could use some help in gathering some additional items. 

Lately we've been struggling with collecting the best bat meat in Hallowfall. Could you gather some before you come to Dunelle's Kindness?
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Auralia Steelstrike in Dunelle's Kindness.
RewardText: Excellent. We just haven't had the resources to pull people off the wall to gather the meat with all those wasps around.
